Package: porowhitahauwha
Title: Interact With Data About Facilities and Partners Within the Connected Communities Portfolio
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lee", "Durbin", , "lee.durbin@aucklandcouncil.govt.nz", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Auckland Council", role = c("cph"))
    )
Description: This package allows authorised staff at Auckland Council to read
    from and write to Porowhita Hauwhā, a database that stores information about
    facilities, partners, and related data that falls within the Connected Communities
    portfolio.
